=== Simple HR between two paragraphs.
--- creole
Hello world.

----

Hello again.
--- html
<p>Hello world.</p>
<hr />
<p>Hello again.</p>

=== Simple HR between two paragraphs without blank lines.
--- creole
Hello world.
----
Hello again.
--- html
<p>Hello world.
----
Hello again.</p>

=== No blank line after HR
--- creole
Hello world.

----
Hello again.
--- html
